Radix fere simplex annua, interdum perennans, rarius crassiuscula et (ut auctores quidam contendunt) perennis (5³). Caules digitales v. ultra fere prostrati, teretes, superne interdum compressi, inferne glabrescentes, su- perne fere pubescentes v. glanduloso-pubescentes. Folia complanata sub- lineari-ffliformia, subulam-mucronata, glaucescentia fere glabra, internodiis sub- aequalia. Stipulae longae lanceolatae attenuato-acuminatas, saepissime lacerae v. partitae fere nitidae. Pedunculi floriferi foliis fulti, summi rarius aphylli, omnes capsula duplo v. triplo longiores. Sepala oblonga obtusiuscula, mar- gine saepe late scariosa. Petala subovata obtusa, calycem fere aequantia, rubra v. lilacina. Oapsula calycem aequans, ovata obtusiuscula.
